+---
+aliases:
+  - configurable vault client timeout
+status: draft
+created: 2026-05-17
+---
+# Story [[platform-flow]] [[product]]
+
+## role
+[[pn002|platform-engineer]]
+
+## want
+configure the vault client timeout per region instead of the hardcoded
+5000ms default
+
+## because
+the European region routinely sees vault round-trips above 5s during
+peak, causing spurious `VaultError`s; the TODO in `src/lib/vault.py`
+captures this gap left out of [[sp001]]
+
+## acceptance_criteria
+- Vault client exposes a `set_timeout(timeout_ms)` configuration entry
+- Per-region overrides resolved at process start
+- Unit test covers timeout-applied and default-fallback behavior
+
+---
+
+Index: [[product]]
